visibility-deliverables/
*-private.pdf

# OS / archive cruft
*.bak
*.tmp
*.orig

# Plugin packaging artifacts (the .plugin zip is built from source, no need to commit)
*.plugin

# Local setup notes — should not ship in the public repo
_PUSH_INSTRUCTIONS.md
_*.md
